    <body><div type="letter">
      <p>Sundy Night</p>
      <p>I had a very suffering night last night. I have scrambled on pretty well today.</p>
      <p>Mr Barwell attends pretty which I feel a comfort. I took a</p>
      <p>drive this evg &amp; liked it.-- I feel very done up, &amp; scarcely care to see or speak much to people, now.</p>
      <p>I fancy myself a little stronger this evg.</p>
      <p>The [too faint to read] not altogether hopeless I think. More promising than the other.</p>
    </div></body>
